690
00:32:12,640 --> 00:32:14,860
we will punish him severely.

691
00:32:18,000 --> 00:32:18,730
How about

692
00:32:19,030 --> 00:32:20,420
you all go back to work first,

693
00:32:20,680 --> 00:32:21,460
and we can

694
00:32:21,830 --> 00:32:23,420
