- Say it here!

710
00:32:48,680 --> 00:32:49,620
Alright.

711
00:32:51,680 --> 00:32:52,460
Here's the thing.

712
00:32:53,030 --> 00:32:54,620
The demands you've made

713
00:32:55,160 --> 00:32:56,980
need the boss's approval.

714
00:32:57,640 --> 00:32:58,290
