717
00:33:02,240 --> 00:33:03,940
Go back to work first.

718
00:33:04,440 --> 00:33:05,140
In a couple of days,

719
00:33:06,000 --> 00:33:07,420
I'll go negotiate with the boss.

720
00:33:07,640 --> 00:33:08,810
