743
00:34:55,440 --> 00:34:56,570
No, that's enough.

744
00:34:56,840 --> 00:34:58,050
Yes, we have to thank you.

745
00:34:58,510 --> 00:34:59,530
Everyone, please dig in.

746
00:35:00,840 --> 00:35:01,900
Come on.

747
00:35:02,480 --> 00:35:02,820
Come on.

748
00:35:04,820 --> 00:35:05,380
It's delicious.

749
00:35:07,070 --> 00:35:07,820
So tasty.

750
00:35:09,030 --> 00:35:09,690
Have some too.

751
00:35:16,380 --> 00:35:17,900
Zhu Sha!

752
00:35:18,300 --> 00:35:19,690
Mr. Huang wants you in his office.

753
00:35:32,360 --> 00:35:33,380
It's okay.

754
00:35:35,190 --> 00:35:36,530
Take care.

755
00:35:45,590 --> 00:35:47,690
The factory has just made a decision.

756
00:35:48,840 --> 00:35:49,860
Effective immediately,

757
00:35:50,710 --> 00:35:53,340
you are no longer employed.

758
00:35:53,480 --> 00:35:56,530
Go to the finance department
to settle your wages,

759
00:35:57,230 --> 00:35:57,980
and then you can leave.

760
00:36:00,070 --> 00:36:01,980
