764
00:36:08,590 --> 00:36:09,980
Don't think that firing me

765
00:36:10,000 --> 00:36:11,260
will solve all your problems.

766
00:36:11,630 --> 00:36:13,010
After this strike,

767
00:36:13,630 --> 00:36:14,740
the female workers already know

768
00:36:14,760 --> 00:36:15,940
how to protect themselves.

769
00:36:16,710 --> 00:36:19,260
And your old methods won't work anymore.

770
00:36:22,710 --> 00:36:23,530
Miss Zhu.

771
00:36:25,480 --> 00:36:28,010
Before you leave,
let me give you a piece of advice.

772
00:36:28,510 --> 00:36:30,610
Trouble comes from talking too much,

773
00:36:31,110 --> 00:36:34,300
and misfortune comes
from sticking your neck out.

774
00:36:36,590 --> 00:36:38,010
Then let me give you one in return.

775
00:36:39,760 --> 00:36:41,050
If you want your business to flourish,

776
00:36:42,190 --> 00:36:43,490
then be a little kinder

777
