782
00:37:00,840 --> 00:37:01,740
you can always trump up a charge.

783
00:37:02,150 --> 00:37:03,090
We've all decided.

784
00:37:03,320 --> 00:37:04,210
We'll strike tomorrow.

785
00:37:04,400 --> 00:37:05,420
We'll get you to stay.

786
00:37:05,590 --> 00:37:06,380
- That's right.
- Exactly.

787
00:37:06,400 --> 00:37:07,490
We'll strike again.

788
00:37:07,510 --> 00:37:08,980
No, please don't.

789
00:37:09,360 --> 00:37:09,940
Why?

790
00:37:10,150 --> 00:37:12,420
The reason the factory was so quick

791
00:37:12,440 --> 00:37:13,570
to agree to our demands before

792
00:37:13,760 --> 00:37:14,940
is that they had a rush order

793
00:37:14,960 --> 00:37:15,780
from Britain.

794
00:37:16,230 --> 00:37:17,420
They couldn't afford
a delay in the schedule.

795
00:37:18,070 --> 00:37:19,650
Now the order is complete,

796
00:37:19,800 --> 00:37:21,170
and they don't have
any deadline pressure.

797
00:37:21,590 --> 00:37:23,740
If you choose to strike now,

798
00:37:24,110 --> 00:37:25,900
they'll just fire you all

799
00:37:26,030 --> 00:37:27,380
and bring in new workers.

800
00:37:29,550 --> 00:37:30,010
Then...

801
00:37:32,760 --> 00:37:34,090
So you're just leaving like this?

802
00:37:34,710 --> 00:37:36,460
What else can I do?

803
00:37:37,000 --> 00:37:38,090
