805
00:37:40,880 --> 00:37:41,900
I don't want you to go.

806
00:37:49,000 --> 00:37:50,380
Don't make it so sad.

807
00:37:50,880 --> 00:37:52,170
We all live in Shanghai.

808
00:37:52,760 --> 00:37:53,490
We'll

809
00:37:53,960 --> 00:37:55,380
meet again sooner or later.

810
00:37:55,800 --> 00:37:56,460
I'm leaving.

811
00:37:57,510 --> 00:37:58,210
Zhu Sha.

812
00:38:01,590 --> 00:38:02,210
Cuiying.

813
00:38:04,400 --> 00:38:05,570
You must never get used to this.

814
00:38:06,070 --> 00:38:07,050
You must make changes.

815
00:38:07,630 --> 00:38:09,050
As long as we stand together,

816
00:38:09,230 --> 00:38:10,490
there's nothing to be afraid of.

817
00:38:12,110 --> 00:38:13,610
