where you're going?

818
00:38:16,030 --> 00:38:16,860
I don't know either.

819
00:38:17,550 --> 00:38:18,490
But I believe

820
00:38:18,510 --> 00:38:20,210
I will find a place for myself.

821
00:38:20,940 --> 00:38:22,650
I also believe

822
00:38:22,670 --> 00:38:23,690
I have a brighter future ahead.

823
00:38:35,590 --> 00:38:36,300
Ladies,

824
00:38:37,980 --> 00:38:38,820
I'll see you again!

825
00:39:05,550 --> 00:39:06,300
Thank you.

826
00:39:19,840 --> 00:39:20,490
Zhu Sha.

827
00:39:25,280 --> 00:39:26,260
What are you doing here?

828
00:39:27,670 --> 00:39:29,490
You quit, and so did I.

829
00:39:29,840 --> 00:39:30,460
Why?

830
00:39:32,440 --> 00:39:34,050
The boss is too heartless.

831
00:39:37,190 --> 00:39:38,650
Which factory isn't like that?

832
00:39:39,630 --> 00:39:41,860
But I don't really buy it.

833
00:39:43,150 --> 00:39:43,740
I...

834
00:39:44,800 --> 00:39:47,050
I was afraid that Lu Agui and his guys
would give you a hard time again,

835
00:39:48,000 --> 00:39:49,210
so I came here to wait for you.

836
00:39:52,590 --> 00:39:54,170
But even if they did come to me,

837
00:39:55,190 --> 00:39:56,530
what could a kid like you do?

838
00:39:57,320 --> 00:39:58,340
I'm not a kid.

839
00:39:58,550 --> 00:39:59,570
I'm nine years old.

840
00:40:00,000 --> 00:40:01,050
I couldn't even tell.

841
00:40:01,320 --> 00:40:02,420
I'm just short.

842
00:40:02,710 --> 00:40:03,820
Don't look down on me.

843
00:40:04,190 --> 00:40:05,090
I didn't.

844
00:40:05,280 --> 00:40:06,010
Let me ask you,

845
00:40:06,510 --> 00:40:07,740
do you have anywhere to go now?

846
00:40:12,280 --> 00:40:13,170
Not really.

847
00:40:13,800 --> 00:40:14,740
Then come with me.

848
00:40:15,230 --> 00:40:15,940
Where to?

849
00:40:16,960 --> 00:40:17,980
You'll know when we get there.

850
00:40:18,070 --> 00:40:18,780
Come with me.

851
00:40:36,020 --> 00:40:38,340
Zu got a job at a cigarette factory
a couple of days ago.

852
00:40:38,510 --> 00:40:39,380
It includes food and lodging.

853
00:40:39,780 --> 00:40:40,900
So the room is now empty.

854
00:40:41,300 --> 00:40:44,460
Zu's place is like a mansion
around here.

855
00:40:45,030 --> 00:40:46,260
That's why I said you're lucky.

856
00:40:46,820 --> 00:40:48,300
Otherwise, you'd have to live there.

857
00:40:48,670 --> 00:40:49,820
It's not like
I haven't lived there before.

858
00:40:50,780 --> 00:40:51,940
Be careful.

859
00:40:58,190 --> 00:40:58,940
What are you laughing at?

860
00:41:06,000 --> 00:41:06,570
We're almost there.

861
00:41:11,280 --> 00:41:12,740
Wen.

862
00:41:12,960 --> 00:41:13,690
What's wrong?

863
00:41:13,800 --> 00:41:14,650
Get up.

864
00:41:15,670 --> 00:41:17,010
Sleep in the back.

865
00:41:19,190 --> 00:41:20,940
You'll have to make do for now.

866
00:41:21,150 --> 00:41:22,860
I'll find you a proper bed later.

867
00:41:23,480 --> 00:41:24,130
Thanks.

868
00:41:24,280 --> 00:41:25,260
That's all right.

869
00:41:25,590 --> 00:41:27,490
We've survived the worst together.

870
00:41:27,590 --> 00:41:28,460
I'm heading out.

871
00:41:28,590 --> 00:41:29,650
I'll swing by tomorrow.

872
00:41:30,030 --> 00:41:30,820
Take care.

873
00:41:33,780 --> 00:41:35,570
I'll go find a straw mat.

874
00:41:36,190 --> 00:41:37,940
It's so late.
Where are you going to find one?

875
00:41:59,550 --> 00:42:02,010
Where did you get all this stuff?

876
00:42:02,630 --> 00:42:03,570
Asked some friends to help.

877
00:42:04,340 --> 00:42:06,010
You have a lot of friends around here?

878
00:42:06,460 --> 00:42:07,570
I grew up here.

879
00:42:09,380 --> 00:42:11,300
Cheng Hui, where are your parents?

880
00:42:11,980 --> 00:42:13,090
They died a long time ago.

881
00:42:18,820 --> 00:42:20,170
You take the bed tonight.

882
00:42:20,190 --> 00:42:20,940
I'll sleep here.

883
00:42:21,820 --> 00:42:23,420
No, you take the bed.

884
00:42:23,460 --> 00:42:24,380
I'm fine on the floor.

885
00:42:24,550 --> 00:42:26,130
It's okay. Just go with what I say.

886
00:42:26,340 --> 00:42:27,380
I'm used to it.

887
00:42:39,380 --> 00:42:39,900
Here.

888
00:42:40,820 --> 00:42:41,650
I'm good.

889
00:42:47,710 --> 00:42:48,570
What are you doing?

890
00:42:51,110 --> 00:42:53,490
Seeing if I've got enough

891
00:42:53,670 --> 00:42:55,300
to get us through a few days.

892
00:42:55,320 --> 00:42:56,010
Let's be clear.

893
00:42:56,670 --> 00:42:57,380
I don't want you supporting me.

